 Ja sam htjela nju gledati

955
00:29:22,700 --> 00:29:24,040
 kroz dobrotu.

956
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:24,620
 Znači ono,

957
00:29:24,620 --> 00:29:26,120
 kako profesor Ivančić kaže,

958
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:27,440
 gledajte u dubine,

959
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,400
 dubine ljudske nas vole.

960
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,500
 Ja to nisam tada znala,

961
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:31,600
 ali mi je bilo,

962
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:33,080
 hoću nešto dobro u njoj naći.

963
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:35,140
 Ja sam se preme njoj počela tako odnositi

964
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:36,200
 i ona jednom prilikom poslala

965
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:36,960
 meni jednu poruku,

966
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:38,200
 onak službenu, hladnu.

967
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:40,320
 Moramo se naći to i tu zbog posladne.

968
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:41,760
 I sad je onak,

969
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:42,060
 ok,

970
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:43,720
 ja ću njoj poslati

971
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:45,740
 poruku punu ljubavi.

972
00:29:45,740 --> 00:29:48,140
 Nije tad bilo srče kao ovih onih,

973
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,220
 ajde Smajlić,

974
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:49,920
 mi smo si super.

975
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:50,600
 Ne.

976
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:52,360
 Ali ja sam u sebi odlučila,

977
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:54,940
 ću ja nekako duhovno njoj to poslati.

978
00:29:54,940 --> 00:29:56,620
 Ja sam poslala onak riječi,

979
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:57,760
 čuj,

980
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,560
 oprosti,

981
00:29:59,560 --> 00:30:00,920
 možemo li se možda tu ne ide način,

982
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:01,920
 znači ništa posebno.

983
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:06,080
 Ali duhovno sam ja nju gledala s ljubavljivu.

984
00:30:06,080 --> 00:30:07,380
 Kad sam još slala tu poruku,

985
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,120
 to je bilo onak,

986
00:30:08,120 --> 00:30:09,440
 baš evo,

987
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:11,120
 želim ti se s ljubavljivu obratiti.

988
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,800
 I mi ti možeš reći što se dogodilo?

989
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:15,040
 Kak je ona odreagirala?

990
00:30:15,040 --> 00:30:16,420
 Pa dobro.

991
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:19,860
 Ona je mogla vjerovati da si ti zapravo to odjedno.

992
00:30:19,860 --> 00:30:20,520
 Da, da, da.

993
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:23,300
 Ona je ti je meni napisala,

994
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:24,420
 Ivana,

995
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:26,760
 mislim da si krivoj osobi poslala poruku.

996
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:27,320
 Kao pogrej.

997
00:30:27,320 --> 00:30:28,660
 Rekao, ne, ne, tebi sam.

998
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:31,080
 Jer nju je valjno osupno ta sva ljubav.

999
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:33,740
 I ona nije mogla vjerovati da sam ja poslala tu poruku.

1000
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:36,620
 I ja sam odlučila biti drugačija prema njoj.

1001
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:38,400
 I naš odnos se počeo mijenjati.

1002
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,020
 Ona sam to opisala čak i u knjizi,

1003
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:40,680
 jer je onda sam rekla,

1004
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,240
 ako jednog dana prečete ovu knjigu,

1005
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:44,280
 da ću skužiti kako smo postale prijateljice.

1006
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:46,680
 Toliko dobro da sam ja nju htjela da bude kuma,

1007
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,000
 jednom od moje djece.

1008
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:50,740
 Znači, onda je ona tišla van Hrvatske i tako.

1009
00:30:50,800 --> 00:30:53,620
 Ali evo, sve se može kad se hoće,

1010
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:54,880
 pa tako i to opraštanje,

1011
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:57,560
 koje evo, dosta ljudi to krivo poimlje,

1012
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:59,700
 misle da ako oni opraštaju,

1013
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:01,660
 da oni u stvari daju za pravo

1014
00:31:01,660 --> 00:31:03,880
 toj drugoj osobi koja ih je ranila,

1015
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,820
 da ono, aha, sad sam ja tu,

1016
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,500
 kao, ja ću sad pogaziti sebe,

1017
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:09,120
 svoj ego, ono,

1018
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:10,840
 mene je osoba, ali kao,

1019
00:31:10,840 --> 00:31:13,460
 to je nepravedno i sad bi ja trebao oprašnati.

1020
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:15,040
 Ne, opraštamo zbog sebe.

1021
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:17,760
 Jer smo mi ranjeni tuđom povredom

1022
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:20,680
 i mi sebe spašavamo, nećući spašavamo,

1023
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:24,360
 ali omogućavamo život dalje opraštanjem.

1024
00:31:24,360 --> 00:31:26,820
 To je različito od onoga kako vele pomirenje.

1025
00:31:26,820 --> 00:31:29,720
 Do pomirenja dolazi kada druga osoba shvati,

1026
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:32,020
 kad se pokaje i kad želi se pomiriti.

1027
00:31:32,020 --> 00:31:34,460
 E onda tu možemo raditi na nekom odnosu.

1028
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:36,000
 Ali ako mene netko povrijedi,

1029
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:39,880
 to recimo evo sad držim neke radionice za djecu i tako

1030
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,360
 i bitno mi je to opraštanje

1031
00:31:41,360 --> 00:31:44,420
 i ovaj, i onda kažem tu jednu situaciju

1032
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:46,940
 koju sam u stvari naučila od jedne časne sestre

1033
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:48,160
 koju sam došla slušat

1034
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:50,440
 u trenutku kad nisam htjela ništa slušat.

1035
00:31:50,440 --> 00:31:52,540
 Jer upravo me pet minuta prije toga

1036
00:31:52,540 --> 00:31:54,300
 povrijedila jedna osoba koja sam

1037
00:31:54,300 --> 00:31:56,660
 ono, i srce, dušu, tijelo, sve sam joj dala.

1038
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:58,560
 Ne, baš sam bila onak dobar mentor

1039
00:31:58,560 --> 00:32:00,060
 i strpljiv i sve.

1040
00:32:00,060 --> 00:32:01,720
 Ona je mene tako izvrijeđala.

1041
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:03,780
 Da ne dajem joj vrijeme, da se ne trudimo oko nje.

1042
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:05,140
 I onda mi još spustila slušalicu.

1043
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:06,760
 Inak mislim si, koje predavanje?

1044
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:08,320
 Nije koje predavanje me sad ne interesira.

1045
00:32:08,320 --> 00:32:10,420
 Ja idem doma, idem žalit sam u sebe.

1046
00:32:10,420 --> 00:32:10,940
 Da, da, da.

1047
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:11,700
 Ali ništa.

1048
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:12,860
 Ja sam već bila parkirana,

1049
00:32:12,860 --> 00:32:14,280
 ulazila sam u tu dvoranu

1050
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,540
 i ta časna sestra je...

1051
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:16,600
 U stvari, ja sam htjela vidjeti

1052
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:18,000
 časnu sestru na skejtu.

1053
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,120
 Jer to je bila reklama.

1054
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:20,360
 Znači, časna na skejtu.

1055
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:22,380
 Ja sam, ta fisto nisam već bila obraćena,

1056
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:23,660
 ja sam htjela idući vidjeti cirkus.

1057
00:32:24,540 --> 00:32:26,400
 I u stvari, ona je pričala o praštanju.

1058
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:28,400
 Znači, prva tema koja se ona dotakla,

1059
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,980
 ona je ovako nacrtala jedno srce

1060
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:31,760
 i probola ga je olovkom.

1061
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:34,180
 I rekla je, kada vas netko povrijedi,

1062
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:37,180
 pokušajte njihovo srce vidjeti,

1063
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:39,280
 ne njih kao zle ovakve, onakve,

1064
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,340
 koje su vam htjeli napakostiti,

1065
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:41,840
 nego pogledajte njihovo srce

1066
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,640
 koje je probodeno sa šiljcima.

1067
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:46,940
 Jer oni su isto na neki način ranjeni.

1068
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:49,240
 I oni bi možda htjeli sa srcem prići vam,

1069
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:51,560
 ali ne mogu jer ih nešto muči.

1070
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,040
 I onda vam, nažalost, pristupi.

1071
00:32:53,040 --> 00:32:54,580
 Kad je ona to tako jednostavno objasnila,

1072
00:32:54,580 --> 00:32:58,800
 te sekunde sam ja tu djevojku vidjela ranjenu

1073
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:01,040
 sa tim njenim srcem i njenim šiljcima.

1074
00:33:01,040 --> 00:33:04,540
 I onak, ajme, pa ne mogu joj ništa zamjerati.

1075
00:33:04,540 --> 00:33:05,580
 Pa ona je isto ranjena.

1076
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:08,460
 I te sekunde ja sam imala totalno drugi gard

1077
00:33:08,460 --> 00:33:09,520
 prema njoj.

1078
00:33:09,520 --> 00:33:11,740
 I to je bilo jedno suosjećanje.

1079
00:33:11,740 --> 00:33:13,900
 Znači, mislim da osoba bez obzira

1080
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:15,960
 kakvu traumu, naravno, ja nisam doživjela,

1081
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:19,300
 neću reći ne znam kako velike traume u životu.

1082
00:33:19,300 --> 00:33:21,060
 I evo, hvala dragom Bogu da nisam

1083
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:23,940
 znao sam, eto, bila ranjena na druge neke načine.

1084
00:33:23,940 --> 00:33:26,680
 Kroz laž, kroz zabluda i sve ostalo.

1085
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:29,560
 Ali ako čovjek ne spozna,

1086
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:32,460
 znači to je ono što to je djeci u stvari kaže.

1087
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:34,460
 Me rekao, gledaj, kako glavni,

1088
00:33:34,460 --> 00:33:38,040
 kako super junak u filmu rješava

1089
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:39,680
 kad ga neko povrijedi.

1090
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:42,000
 Jel on hoda ostatak filma i kuka,

1091
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:45,480
 glej kak me povrijedio, glej kak me on je tamo zločesti ranio.

1092
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,820
 Ne, on to ne radi.

1093
00:33:46,820 --> 00:33:50,360
 On to, ne znam da li je to sad neki predmet ili nešto,

1094
00:33:50,600 --> 00:33:51,600
 on ga iščupa,

1095
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:54,460
 poveže ranu da može ići spasiti grad.

1096
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:56,920
 Znači, on ne kuka.

1097
00:33:56,920 --> 00:34:00,420
 Ali mi svi, mi smo svi super junaciji u svojim životima.

1098
00:34:00,420 --> 00:34:02,020
 I trebali bi se tako ponašati.

1099
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:03,340
 Ali mi idemo, joj, gledaj mene,

1100
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:04,500
 glej kak sam ja žrtva,

1101
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:06,040
 glej kak je meni teško,

1102
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:07,200
 ja ne umanjujem,

1103
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,520
 nić je, nić je rane.

1104
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:12,360
 Ali moramo spoznati da opraštanjem,

1105
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,800
 mi vadimo taj šiljak iz svog srca,

1106
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,440
 taj otrov,

1107
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,900
 vadimo van,

1108
00:34:16,900 --> 00:34:20,320
 da bi Bog mogao nas zacijeliti.

1109
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,360
 Puno ljudi kaže,

1110
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,420
 da, da, ja se molim,

1111
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:23,860
 sakramentalno živim,

1112
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:25,060
 ali evo, ne mogu uzdraviti,

1113
00:34:25,060 --> 00:34:26,200
 ne mogu ovo, ne mogu ono.

1114
00:34:26,200 --> 00:34:29,140
 I onda dođemo do toga da ta osoba ne može oprostiti.

1115
00:34:29,860 --> 00:34:31,520
 Evo, pričala si sad oprost o drugima,

1116
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:33,500
 a što je oprost pre samom sebi?

1117
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:34,300
 Sebi, da.

1118
00:34:34,300 --> 00:34:36,900
 Znači, baš to, evo,

1119
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:38,180
 to već u srednjoj školi,

1120
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:39,480
 kad sam vidjela sebe,

1121
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,820
 ja sam shvatila da moram,

1122
00:34:40,820 --> 00:34:43,520
 da ja moram neke stvari u sebi promijeniti.

1123
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:44,420
 Ja sam mogla isto,

1124
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,700
 vi, kada vidiš ove mi je ovako,

1125
00:34:45,700 --> 00:34:46,360
 ove mi je ovako,

1126
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:49,100
 ali jednostavno kad čovjek spozna tko je,

1127
00:34:49,100 --> 00:34:50,960
 znači ako ja spoznam danas,

1128
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:52,860
 da sam ja Božje dijete

1129
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:55,480
 i da mi je Bog toliko je omogućio

1130
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:56,340
 i toliko dao,

1131
00:34:56,420 --> 00:34:59,540
 a ja spriječavam svojim odlukama,

1132
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:02,880
 svojom ustrajnošću

1133
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:05,620
 i na tom spriječavam milosti

1134
00:35:05,620 --> 00:35:07,380
 koje mogu dobiti od dragog Boga.

1135
00:35:07,380 --> 00:35:09,920
 Onda ponašam se veoma nerazumno

1136
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:11,100
 i veoma bedasto.

1137
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:15,320
 I prije sam to gledala na emotivnoj razini

1138
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:17,020
 u stilu, ha, mene niko ne razumije,

1139
00:35:17,020 --> 00:35:17,800
 meni je teško,

1140
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:20,120
 meni je, ja sam imala takav nadimak,

1141
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:21,120
 ne želim ga ovdje reći,

1142
00:35:21,120 --> 00:35:22,640
 jer znam da bi svi umrli od smijeha,

1143
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:24,680
 ali taj nadimak je odrežavao

1144
00:35:24,680 --> 00:35:27,620
 kako sam se ja većinu vremena osjećala.

1145
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:28,980
 Osjećala sam se kiselo,

1146
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:31,020
 osjećala sam se nevoljeno,

1147
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:32,860
 jer je mene jedna riječ tuža

1148
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:34,020
 mogla povrijediti.

1149
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:36,180
 Ali ja sam i sebe onda povrijeđivala

1150
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:39,080
 ustrajući u tome da ja sebe vidim

1151
00:35:39,080 --> 00:35:40,140
 kao žrtvu.

1152
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:41,840
 Znači, kad sam ja vidjela

1153
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,900
 što sam sebi sve napravila

1154
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:45,540
 kroz ovo, kroz ovo, kroz ovo,

1155
00:35:45,540 --> 00:35:47,960
 bojme čovjek mora sjesti sam sa sobom.

1156
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:50,200
 Zašto ostavimo u stanju te žrtve?

1157
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:52,180
 Pa zato što je to lakše.

1158
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:54,560
 Evo, iskreno moram reći lakše,

1159
00:35:54,560 --> 00:35:57,040
 ali upoznala sam i na svom primjeru,

1160
00:35:57,040 --> 00:35:59,400
 lakše mi je ukriviti drugoga.

1161
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:01,120
 Pa mislim, Adam i Eva su to napravili.

1162
00:36:01,120 --> 00:36:02,800
 Ako su oni to napravili,

1163
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:05,100
 naravno, to je u našim genima ću reći

1164
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:06,640
 i protiv toga se moramo boriti.

1165
00:36:06,640 --> 00:36:09,040
 Znači, mi bi danas živjeli u raju

1166
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:10,580
 da su samo Adam i Eva rekli

1167
00:36:10,580 --> 00:36:12,740
 sorry, fakat sam pogriješio.

1168
00:36:12,740 --> 00:36:14,020
 Ali, ne.

1169
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:16,600
 Rađuću prstom upriti u drugoga.

1170
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:18,740
 Ako mi gledamo sebe,

1171
00:36:18,740 --> 00:36:20,720
 onda ćemo vidjeti puno manjkavosti.

1172
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,380
 Znači, meni nije bilo ugodno.

1173
00:36:22,380 --> 00:36:24,080
 Ja ne bi nikad pustila taj film

1174
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,880
 da ja vidim kak sam ja povrijedila drugoga.

1175
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:27,400
 Meni je to bilo pušteno.

1176
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,800
 Ali nakon toga,

1177
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:30,100
 kad bi me neko upozorio,

1178
00:36:30,100 --> 00:36:31,080
 e, ovo ti ne valja.

1179
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,820
 Ok, stop, alarm.

1180
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:34,740
 Sjedni, pogledaj sebe.

1181
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,020
 Znači, jednostavno,

1182
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:37,780
 ja sam se htjela mijenjati.

1183
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:38,720
 Ja sam htjela,

1184
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:39,840
 ja sam htjela ozdraviti.

1185
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:41,600
 Pa, evo, bila je tako jedna situacija

1186
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:43,340
 gdje sam baš jednom djevojkom razgovarala

1187
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:44,680
 privatno, ne.

1188
00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:45,840
 I baš im onako,

1189
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,460
 ujednoj, imala sam kao neku vizigu

1190
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:48,140
 gdje sam ju vidjela.

1191
00:36:48,140 --> 00:36:50,180
 Ja rekao, pa ti si kao u jednom kavezu.

1192
00:36:50,180 --> 00:36:53,200
 Ali ti zaista možeš otvoriti taj kavez, ne.

1193
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:55,640
 I zaći van i biti slobodna ozdraviti.

1194
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:58,260
 I ona veli, a što ću onda?

1195
00:36:58,260 --> 00:37:00,820
 Što ću onda kada izađem iz tog kaveza?

1196
00:37:05,240 --> 00:37:05,960
 Ne brinu za mene.

1197
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,580
 A ova treća mi je čak,

1198
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:09,360
 i kad ja to tako slušam od njih,

1199
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:11,040
 ono mogu čak jednu priču povezat.

1200
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:13,480
 Jedna je bila ranjena od strane.

1201
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,440
 Roditelja je rekla je,

1202
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:17,320
 neka sad oni pate kao što ja patim.

1203
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:19,540
 Znači, nema opraštanja.

1204
00:37:19,540 --> 00:37:21,200
 Znači, bez obzira što ta djevojka

1205
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:22,680
 i sakramentalno živi,

1206
00:37:22,680 --> 00:37:24,780
 i svećenici su molili,

1207
00:37:24,780 --> 00:37:26,140
 išla je u svetišta,

1208
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:27,120
 išla je ovdje, ondje,

1209
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:28,120
 ide na ispovjed.

1210
00:37:28,120 --> 00:37:30,200
 Moli se ona, dragome Bogu,

1211
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:32,220
 ali dragi Bog, ne može joj dati milost

1212
00:37:32,220 --> 00:37:33,900
 i ne može napraviti ništa,

1213
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:35,920
 jer ona nije donijela odluku.

1214
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:36,600
 I onda ljudi misle,

1215
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,200
 aha, ja moram osjetiti neku emociju.

1216
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:39,260
 Ne emociju.

1217
00:37:39,260 --> 00:37:40,740
 Bitna je odluka.

1218
00:37:40,740 --> 00:37:42,180
 Emotivno, pa i džavo,

1219
00:37:42,180 --> 00:37:45,860
 džavo može veoma utjecat na naše emocije.

1220
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:48,740
 On barata našom psihofizičkom razinom

1221
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:50,580
 i može nas tu veoma zavisi.

1222
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:51,460
 Tako da emocije,

1223
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:53,520
 ne smemo se baš u njih pouzdati,

1224
00:37:53,520 --> 00:37:55,240
 ali odluka.

1225
00:37:55,240 --> 00:37:58,680
 Znači, ja odlučujem oprostiti toj osobi.

1226
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:00,440
 I kad mi odlučimo,

1227
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:02,020
 vadimo taj šiljak vani,

1228
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:04,160
 onda Bog može napraviti na nama

1229
00:38:04,160 --> 00:38:06,080
 operaciju i zahvate.

1230
00:38:06,080 --> 00:38:07,300
 Lijepo si to rekla.

1231
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:09,260
 I za kraj pitanje,

1232
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:10,520
 evo, rekla si mi,

1233
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:13,020
 prije podcasta kad smo razgovarali,

1234
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:15,560
 odlučilo sam biti doma sa svojom djecom.

1235
00:38:15,560 --> 00:38:18,080
 Da, znači,

1236
00:38:18,080 --> 00:38:20,560
 Obert, moja knjiga,

1237
00:38:20,560 --> 00:38:22,420
 promocija po Hrvatskoj,

1238
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:23,820
 ja držim predavanja,

1239
00:38:23,820 --> 00:38:24,940
 po svuku da sam,

1240
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:26,440
 držim predavanja o prehrani,

1241
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,860
 pričamo o treningu.

1242
00:38:27,860 --> 00:38:29,560
 Znači, ja po svuku da.

1243
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:30,740
 Ja imam svoj biznis,

1244
00:38:30,900 --> 00:38:33,800
 nakon što se mala Dona rodila,

1245
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,300
 to je to,

1246
00:38:34,300 --> 00:38:36,280
 tri godine imam pravo biti s njom doma,

1247
00:38:36,280 --> 00:38:37,160
 nakon toga,

1248
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,300
 ja dalje,

1249
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,400
 po svome,

1250
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,700
 jer to je ono što ja želim,

1251
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:41,840
 ja želim pomagati ljudima.

1252
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,500
 I dogodi se jedna situacija,

1253
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:44,800
 gdje im jedna prijateljica pozove

1254
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:47,180
 na jednu veće dobročinitelja.

1255
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:48,420
 Ja rekao,

1256
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:49,160
 Bože, dragi,

1257
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:50,740
 u ovom trenutku ne javni ti kune,

1258
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:53,320
 sad ona mene zove na veće dobročinitelje.

1259
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:53,700
 Pa rekao,

1260
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:54,220
 pa dobro,

1261
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:54,440
 ajde,

1262
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:55,180
 kak me već zove,

1263
00:38:55,180 --> 00:38:55,400
 valina,

1264
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:55,820
 dragi Bog,

1265
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:56,400
 zna zašto.

1266
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:58,000
 Kak sam odlučila biti poslušna,

1267
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:58,220
 sada,

1268
00:38:58,220 --> 00:38:59,000
 dragome Bogu,

1269
00:38:59,000 --> 00:38:59,860
 jer sam rekla,

1270
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:00,820
 budi volja tvoja,

1271
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:02,860
 sad to stvarno tako vrijedi u mom životu.

1272
00:39:02,860 --> 00:39:03,060
 Rekao,

1273
00:39:03,060 --> 00:39:03,240
 ajde,

1274
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:03,940
 bit ću poslušna

1275
00:39:03,940 --> 00:39:04,720
 i odem ja tamo,

1276
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:05,840
 ne znam od kud sam novce opće,

1277
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:06,900
 nejako je skemijela.

1278
00:39:07,580 --> 00:39:08,980
 i ona mene,

1279
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:09,820
 prvo pitanje,

1280
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:11,180
 i što radiš u životu?

1281
00:39:11,180 --> 00:39:12,000
 I rekao,

1282
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,400
 po ništa,

1283
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:12,780
 evo ga,

1284
00:39:12,780 --> 00:39:14,220
 mala mi je sada doma,

1285
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:14,920
 samo ovo ono,

1286
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:15,440
 tri godine,

1287
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:17,600
 i sad ja svoj veliki poslovni plan.

1288
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:19,000
 Ona mene samo pogleda,

1289
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:19,240
 veli,

1290
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:19,860
 ok,

1291
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:21,340
 ne bi ti bila doma s djecom?

1292
00:39:21,340 --> 00:39:23,560
 Znači,

1293
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:24,240
 mi smo se vidjeli,

1294
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:25,740
 možda deset godina nas dvije.

1295
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:26,700
 Ali ona onak,

1296
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:27,980
 kod je sam dragi Bog,

1297
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:28,300
 posla,

1298
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:28,500
 ok,

1299
00:39:28,500 --> 00:39:29,220
 imaš misiju,

1300
00:39:29,220 --> 00:39:29,960
 trebaš Ivanu,

1301
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:32,080
 trebaš još nešto reći.

1302
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:33,820
 I kad je ona počela pričat,

1303
00:39:33,880 --> 00:39:35,240
 kak je ona s tom djecom doma?

1304
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:37,280
 Ona ih ima četvero.

1305
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:39,140
 Kako ona ide s njima u park?

1306
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:40,380
 Kako ona se s njima igra?

1307
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:41,000
 Kako ona radi?

1308
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:43,480
 U meni je nešto se rodilo,

1309
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,180
 nešto,

1310
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:44,580
 ono,

1311
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:46,320
 kod je neko nešto zapalio,

1312
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:46,600
 ono,

1313
00:39:46,600 --> 00:39:48,700
 nešto što u stvari u meni postoji,

1314
00:39:48,700 --> 00:39:49,520
 a ja sam stalno,

1315
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:50,300
 ma ne, ne,

1316
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,180
 nisam ja za to.

1317
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:53,480
 Ok, ja jesam stvarno htjela to troje djece,

1318
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:54,920
 Bog me promijenio ih tijela,

1319
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:59,580
 ali nisam mislila da sam sad osoba koja će sjediti doma s djecom.

1320
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,820
 Sjediti doma ne znači sjediti doma,

1321
00:40:01,820 --> 00:40:04,160
 nego zaista se angažirati oko te djece,

1322
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:04,820
 to mi je bilo onak,

1323
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:06,140
 ne, ne, ja idem raditi,

1324
00:40:06,140 --> 00:40:07,160
 imam ja svog posla,

1325
00:40:07,160 --> 00:40:08,000
 nema ja vala s djecom,

1326
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:08,960
 neki idu oni u vrtić,

1327
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,700
 neki idu u školu i to je to, ne.

1328
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:12,900
 I kad je ona to počela govorit,

1329
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:15,680
 ja sam došla doma i to je mene obuzelo.

1330
00:40:15,680 --> 00:40:17,180
 Ja sam mjesec dana,

1331
00:40:17,180 --> 00:40:19,580
 to je sad bila borba sa samom sobom,

1332
00:40:19,580 --> 00:40:21,600
 jer kak sad ja, poduzetna,

1333
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:22,520
 ja imam plan,

1334
00:40:22,520 --> 00:40:23,920
 ja pomažem ljudima,

1335
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,360
 ja ovo, ja po svuku da,

1336
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:26,500
 onak ne,

1337
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:29,120
 ti ćeš sad biti doma s djecom.

1338
00:40:29,120 --> 00:40:32,280
 Ja sam mjesec dana stvarno bila u mukama,

1339
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:33,340
 ali to je već bilo,

1340
00:40:33,340 --> 00:40:34,260
 to je već bilo zapaljeno,

1341
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:34,980
 to je bilo gotovo,

1342
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:36,940
 ja sam sam to morala prihvatit.

1343
00:40:36,940 --> 00:40:39,080
 I ja sam došla rekla,

1344
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:40,240
 ja zatvaram overt.

1345
00:40:40,240 --> 00:40:41,820
 Ja sam se normalno sa suprugom

1346
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:42,980
 u dogovoru s njim,

1347
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:43,900
 ništa, to nisam sama,

1348
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:45,320
 ali on je isto vidio

1349
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:47,320
 to nešto u meni

1350
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:48,820
 i on je mene podržao u tome

1351
00:40:48,820 --> 00:40:49,640
 i ja sam odlučila

1352
00:40:49,640 --> 00:40:51,240
 ostati doma s djecom.

1353
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,880
 nisam zažaljela niti minute

1354
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:55,660
 da evo danas kad ono,

1355
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:58,160
 ja koja sam čak držala seminare

1356
00:40:58,160 --> 00:41:00,340
 o tome kako žena treba biti poduzetna,

1357
00:41:00,340 --> 00:41:02,000
 kako ona treba izaći,

1358
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:04,200
 napraviti sve svoje ciljeve

1359
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:05,400
 koje ima ovo ono, ne,

1360
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:07,240
 ostvariti se kao žena,

1361
00:41:07,240 --> 00:41:08,320
 ne kao žena,

1362
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,740
 nego kao poduzetnica.

1363
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:11,920
 i to mi je bilo onako,

1364
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:13,280
 to ću ja svakoj ženi

1365
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:14,500
 dobro objasniti,

1366
00:41:14,500 --> 00:41:16,420
 da sad ja sjedim doma,

1367
00:41:16,420 --> 00:41:17,840
 sjedim, opet kažem sjedim,

1368
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:19,300
 ali to nije sjedenje doma,

1369
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:21,460
 da se ja angažiram oko svoje djece,

1370
00:41:21,460 --> 00:41:22,860
 da ja činim stvari

1371
00:41:22,860 --> 00:41:24,880
 koje moji roditelji sa mnom nisu činili,

1372
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,880
 da je moj sin došao

1373
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:26,400
 i meni veli,

1374
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:27,880
 mama, ja znam

1375
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:29,420
 zakaj ti nas toliko grliš,

1376
00:41:29,420 --> 00:41:30,740
 zakaj nas toliko ljubiš

1377
00:41:30,740 --> 00:41:32,620
 i zakaj se moliš s nama svaku večer.

1378
00:41:32,620 --> 00:41:34,200
 Ja je rekao daj mi otkrit tajnu,

1379
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:35,380
 tad imamo negdje pet godina,

1380
00:41:35,380 --> 00:41:36,100
 sad ima osam.

1381
00:41:36,680 --> 00:41:39,000
 Velijon, zato što su to tebi

1382
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:40,500
 tvoji roditelji činili.

1383
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:43,040
 Iskreno, u toj sekundi

1384
00:41:43,040 --> 00:41:44,920
 nisam mu htjela odmah probiti

1385
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,840
 taj njegov sretni balončić,

1386
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:49,100
 porazgovarala sam se sa gospodinom,

1387
00:41:49,100 --> 00:41:50,920
 rekao sam, da ja to njemu ipak kažem

1388
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,100
 i onda shvatim onako, pa da,

1389
00:41:52,100 --> 00:41:54,400
 pa moram poslije doći za gospodina.

1390
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,340
 Ja je rekao, sine,

1391
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:56,720
 to nisu sa mnom radili,

1392
00:41:56,720 --> 00:41:58,280
 niko nije sa mnom molio svaku večer,

1393
00:41:58,280 --> 00:41:59,380
 niko me nije grlio ovako

1394
00:41:59,380 --> 00:42:00,620
 kao što ja vas grlim

1395
00:42:00,620 --> 00:42:02,020
 i preko dane, preko noći

1396
00:42:02,020 --> 00:42:02,820
 i preko uvijek.

1397
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:05,780
 je rekao, to mi je Isus napravio.

1398
00:42:05,780 --> 00:42:08,040
 Znači, Isus mi je dao tu ljubav

1399
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:10,020
 i zbog toga što ja imam njegovu ljubav,

1400
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:11,660
 ja mogu tu ljubav dati vama.

1401
00:42:11,660 --> 00:42:12,500
 Tako da sam, evo,

1402
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:14,120
 zaista sretna što mogu biti doma.

1403
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:14,560
 Lijepo.

1404
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:16,640
 Ja sam zaista sretna što si došla u podcast.

1405
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:17,960
 Evo, hvala što si.

1406
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:19,260
 I zato ti želimo zahvaliti

1407
00:42:19,260 --> 00:42:20,520
 jednim malim poklončićem.

1408
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:22,960
 Hvala ti, Ivana, što si došla.

1409
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:23,340
 Hvala vam.

1410
00:42:23,340 --> 00:42:25,160
 A sve vas darovat ćemo

1411
00:42:25,160 --> 00:42:26,660
 jednim predivnim nakitom

1412
00:42:26,660 --> 00:42:27,480
 no ka boel.

1413
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:29,720
 Tako da pratite nas

1414
00:42:33,940 --> 00:42:34,440
 Mak!

